The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for inferring concept hierarchies from text corpora. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses hyperbolic embeddings, which are a type of geometric deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category. The paper also deals with information retrieval and text mining, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of constraints and optimization techniques, making cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) a possible category as well.
